ulimit -n 65536
ulimit -s 10240
ulimit -c unlimited

I. vi /etc/security/limits.conf
root             -       nofile          65536

II. vi /etc/security/limits.conf
root             -       stack	         10240

III. vi /etc/security/limits.conf
root             -       core	         unlimited

Example
root             -       nofile          65536
root             -       stack	         10240
root             -       core	         unlimited
